<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sample HTML Page</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    header {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    main {
      margin: 20px auto;
      max-width: 800px;
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Welcome to My Sample Page</h1>
  </header>

  <main>
    <h2>About This Page</h2>
    <p>This is a simple HTML page example. You can use this template to start building your own website.</p>
    <p>It includes a header, main content area, and footer, all styled with basic CSS.</p>

    <h3>Features</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Responsive layout</li>
      <li>Simple CSS styling</li>
      <li>Clean structure</li>
    </ul>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 My Sample Site</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
